[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……というわけで、第１回九偉人会は\nあっけなく解散となったのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01002",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "クレオによると、ヘルトは牢に戻った後も\nまだ元気ないみたいだし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01003",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "逆にゼロは騒いでいるから、\n困ってるみたいだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01004",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "とりあえず、お疲れ、相棒。\n癖の強い九偉人全員を集めるなんて、よくやったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01005",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "ヘルトが魂抜けたままってのは困るが\n九偉人全員で飯食うなんて、大きな進歩じゃねえか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01006",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "少し前じゃ、考えられない進歩よね。\nよくやったわ、私！　……でもやっぱり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01007",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "なんだ、ヘルトが心配なのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01008",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん。ご飯を食べれば元気になると思ったんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01009",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そりゃ、相棒はそうかもしれないけど、\nヘルトはヴァレリアじゃないからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01010",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "俺たちは、天使ちゃんのうまいご飯に何度も\n心も身体も支えてもらってきたけどな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01011",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ！\nいつもありがとう、フロッケ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01012",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……でもまぁ、そっか。\nみんながみんな、食事で元気になるとは限らないのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01013",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトがどうしてああなっているのか、\n何を考えているのか、分かればいいんだけれど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01014",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "どうしてああなってるか、相棒は分からないの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01015",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん……だってヘルト、話してくれないし。\nそれについ最近、初めて会ったばっかりの相手だし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01016",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "今のヘルトは様子がおかしいっていうのは分かるけど\nそれがどうしてなのかまでは分からないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01017",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "負けたのはショックだろうけど、\nそれだけにしては重症すぎるような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01018",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "それならよ、まずはヘルトの周りの奴に、\n色々と話を聞いてみたらどうだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01019",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "周りの奴……っていうと、やっぱり兄弟たちかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01020",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "ああ。仲間や家族っていうのは、\nお互いのことを見ているもんだからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01021",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "船員に何か抱え込んじまった奴が出たときは、\n周囲の奴に聞いてみると糸口が見えてきたもんだぜ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01022",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そうだね。本人たちには分からない夫婦ゲンカの\n原因も、娘から見たら一目瞭然だったりするもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01023",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そっか。私やシトリンに分からなくても、\n他の兄弟から見れば分かるかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01024",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとう、二人とも！\n私、兄弟たちにヘルトの話を聞きに行ってみるわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01025",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトの話を聞くなら、やっぱ最初はゼロかしら？\n一緒に行動してるっぽかったし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01026",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "早速クレオにお願いして、会ってくる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01027",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ちょ、こんな時間に行くなバカ！\n王女サマを怒らせるようなことしちゃまずいって！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01028",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "クレオ姫ならこんな時間でも許してくれそうだけど……\n相棒が帰って来たら説教してやらないと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01029",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "きっとあいつは、ヘルトの様子を直接見ている分、\nヘルトのことが一層心配なんだろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01030",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "非常識なことに変わりはないが、\n心が急く理由も分かる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01031",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……そうだね。\n相棒、あのゼロ相手に大丈夫かなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_01032",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "なんだかんだ言っても、あいつらは家族だ。\nきっと大丈夫だろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01033",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "もし、あいつが落ち込んで帰って来たら、\nみんなで天使ちゃんのうまい飯を食おう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01034",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "俺たちだって家族だからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_037_01035",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]